annotationA: Sphingolipid delta-4 desaturase activity; stearoyl-CoA 9-desaturase activity. It is involved in the biological process described with: spermatogenesis; sphingolipid biosynthetic process; spindle assembly involved in male meiosis
annotationB: Wunen-2, isoform A; Wunen-2 is a lipid phosphate phosphatase, an enzyme with an active site predicted to face extracellularly. It is required for germ cell migration and survival, acting partially redundantly with its paralog wun
